"Rab-e-Azan-e-Bilali bhi Tu,
 Arham bhi tu aur Jalali bhi Tu...
..
Tu Rab-e-Mustafa,
Tu Rab-e-Murtaza,
Rab-e-Sirat-e-Mustaqeem,
Tu Rab-e-Kaa'ba

Nooh ki Kashti Ku dekhta hon,
Hoz-e-Nidamat maen doba hoa hon..
...

Rab-e-Dewar-e-Zulqarnain bhi Tu,
Rab-e-Mairaj-e-Kona'in bhi Tu,
Rab-e-Ismail-o-ZamZam bhi Tu,

Tu Rab-e-Ibrahim,
Tu Rab-e-Jibrail,
Rab-e-Malaika,
Tu Rab-e-Kosar.
Apny Ghulamon,
ki day gulami,
Ya mutakabir..
...
Roz-e-Hashar ka andaza nai,
Bakhshish ka saman laya nahi,
Hy meri iltija,
Kr de qurbat aata,
Kr de Rehm-o-karam.......

Mere Irady Ju totay tu mujku pata ye chala,
Teri hakomat maen huga bs ju tu ny kaha,
apnay Habib k sadqy maen sun ly mere ye dua.....

Rab-e-Zarb-e-Haider Hamza bhi Tu,
Rab-e-A'ssa-e-Musa bhi Tu,
Tu Robaro bhi aur hy ko ba ko..

Tu Rab-e-Essa,
Tu Rab-e-Maryam,
Rab-e-Sahaba,
Tu Rab-e-Panjtan,
Nooh ki Kashti,
Ku dekhta hon,
Hoz e nidamat..maen dooba hoa hon..."
